<td class="tableblock halign-left valign-top"><p class="tableblock">Click on <strong>Search</strong> without selecting any filter settings. This will display all customer reviews. Alternatively, limit the search results by using filters and click on <strong>Search</strong>. The customer reviews found will be listed in the overview.</p></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td class="tableblock halign-left valign-top"><p class="tableblock"><strong>Reset</strong></p></td>
<td class="tableblock halign-left valign-top"><p class="tableblock">Resets the filter criteria that was entered.</p></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td class="tableblock halign-left valign-top"><p class="tableblock"><strong>Feedback ID</strong></p></td>
<td class="tableblock halign-left valign-top"><p class="tableblock">Each customer review automatically receives a consecutive and unique ID. The ID is always a real number. <strong>00521</strong> or <strong>ADF8354</strong> e.g. are invalid.</p></td>
